"34:5:5" : {s: 34, a: 5, w: 5, r: "عجز", t: "مُعَٰجِزِينَ", l: "مُعَٰجِزِين", lc: 3, tl: "muʿājizīna", lb: "অক্ষমকারী",e: "(to) cause failure", b: "ব্যর্থকারী", i: "melemahkan/menentang", f: 3, rm: "to become behind, lack, become in the rear, lag behind (strength), become incapable, powerless, be weak. ujuzun - old women. ajaza (vb. 4) to weaken, frustrate, find one to be weak. muajiz - one who baffles. ajzun (pl. ajazun) - portion of the trunk that is below its upper part."},
